{"tid":1025470,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"ITZY 3女含金鎖匙出世？LiA讀國際學校一年學費6千萬圜","createTime":"2019-02-17T11:11:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-18T00:32:50.000Z","uid":3189,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"f70c3741207b021a69e6507ff144c0048bb0ed42","tid":1025470,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T11:11:06.000Z","msg":"ITZY 3女含金鎖匙出世？LiA讀國際學校一年學費6千萬圜<br />\n<br />\n看來家境不錯~<br />\n<br />\nJYP新女團ITZY最近以大熱姿態出道，衆人焦點除了放在成員的實力、外貌以及歌曲外，個人資料特別是出道前的經歷也備受各方的關注。3名成員柳真、彩鈴和LiA被爆家境富裕，是含著「金鎖匙」出世。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2019/02/20190215_en_itzy_6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2019%2F02%2F20190215_en_itzy_6.jpg&h=c107766a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n網上圖片<br />\n<br />\n前兩人雖然未有太多成長背景流出，但柳真的家是位於被稱爲有錢人區的江南，而彩鈴出道前在家中的自拍也看出家裏十分大，是豪宅的級別。不過最讓粉絲驚訝的是LiA，應該是3人之中條件最好的那位。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2019/02/20190215_en_itzy_8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2019%2F02%2F20190215_en_itzy_8.jpg&h=d48d6458&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n柳真（網上圖片）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2019/02/20190215_en_itzy_2-e1550199064369.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2019%2F02%2F20190215_en_itzy_2-e1550199064369.png&h=192418e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n彩鈴（網上圖片）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2019/02/20190215_en_itzy_4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2019%2F02%2F20190215_en_itzy_4.jpg&h=83227117&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n彩鈴的家十分大（網上圖片）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2019/02/20190215_en_itzy_1-e1550199070838.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2019%2F02%2F20190215_en_itzy_1-e1550199070838.png&h=3a60a010&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nLiA（網上圖片）<br />\n<br />\nLiA就讀的是英國北倫敦國際學校濟州分校，該校曾經因學費過高受到批評，基本上就是為富家子弟而設。根據粉絲搜集到的資料，學校不但有100個不同的社團活動，學費、住宿費等費用加起來一年要6千萬韓圜，約42萬港元，絕不是一般家庭能夠負擔。在出道前LiA在網上論壇被問到大學會否去英國的時候，她的回答是還不知道要去英國還是美國，結果最後是去了JYP。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2019/02/20190215_en_itzy_7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2019%2F02%2F20190215_en_itzy_7.jpg&h=0dad76f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nLiA就讀的國際學校一年費用達6千萬韓圜（網上圖片）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2019/02/20190215_en_itzy_5-e1550199411284.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2019%2F02%2F20190215_en_itzy_5-e1550199411284.jpg&h=6b730270&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nLiA出道前發回應提問（網上圖片）<br />\n<br />\n隨後更有眼利的粉絲發現，仍是練習生的LiA曾被目擊現身前輩TWICE的演唱會，當時被粉絲拍到的照片中她的手袋的牌子是Prada，果然不簡單。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2019/02/20190215_en_itzy_3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2019%2F02%2F20190215_en_itzy_3.jpg&h=89e7780e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nLiA出道前曾被目擊現身TWICE演唱會，圖中手袋牌子為Prada（網上圖片）"},{"pid":"f1e10475b1cb2ad35d44c75e2f4ac818242efd08","tid":1025470,"uid":223790,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T11:12:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2c36e92dc20304634899a7ebd08494a7e809166a","tid":1025470,"uid":555,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T11:12:42.000Z","msg":"柳真屈到"},{"pid